PrecisTransfer to the Province of QUEBEC of the administration and control over a total of 585 hectares of land situated near MONTREAL INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT, in either the Town of Mirabel or the Town of Lachute, for the purposes of Mirabel Boulevard and Highway No. 50, including 21 small strips of land used for roads or for Highway No. 15 (Laurentian Autoroute).
